title: U of M parking ramp recognized for energy efficiency

Apartment Sales Tracker Home / Brief / U of M parking ramp recognized for energy efficiency The Gortner Avenue Ramp at 1395 Gortner Ave. in St. Paul won awards in the categories of greatest percentage of savings in a single structure, and best use of lighting controls.
